MathTools  (working title)
---------

Tool to demonstrate different aspects of high school
mathematics such as plotting of functions, binomial distribution,
linear algebra computations, testing.

Used language: C++
GUI with Qt 4.
Libraries needed to build and run: gsl (http://www.gnu.org/s/gsl), qt4 (http://qt.nokia.com/products),
                                   ginac (http://www.ginac.de), cln (http://www.ginac.de/CLN)

Build with cmake.

All code is licensed under the GPLv3, see LICENSE.

